OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Ftonight with clear skies for a while,
OL,7,Fwith patchy low cloud pushing in from
OL,8,Fthe east later. Temperatures will fall
OL,9,Funder the clear spells to give a
OL,10,Fpatchy rural frost in sheltered
OL,11,Flocations.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSunday:FAfter a chilly start, it will
OL,14,Fbe another warm day with light winds.
OL,15,FSome bright or sunny spells, but
OL,16,Fcloudier than on Saturday. A small
OL,17,Fchance of a shower later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
